=========================================================================
Third-party binary notice
=========================================================================

Filesystem drivers distributed in dist/EFI/LamBoot/drivers/*.efi (ext4, btrfs,
ntfs, xfs, zfs, f2fs, iso9660) are derived from the rEFInd project and are
licensed GPL-2.0. They are distributed as separate binaries under the GPL
linking exception and are not statically linked into the LamBoot bootloader
binary. The LamBoot bootloader itself contains no GPL-licensed code.

Source for the rEFInd filesystem drivers is available at:
    https://www.rodsbooks.com/refind/

